Trade/Device Name(s): GoChek Connect Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for GoChek and GoChek Connect Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems using amperometric electrochemical method for self-monitoring of blood glucose in people with diabetes.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from the fingertips for self-testing by people with diabetes at home as an aid in monitoring the effectiveness of diabetes control programs; not for diagnosis or screening for diabetes.
